# ResponStay – Smart Crisis Response System for Hospitality

## Overview
ResponStay is an AI-powered emergency response system designed for hotels to improve crisis handling and coordination in real time.

## Problem
Traditional emergency systems in hotels are slow and lack coordination, leading to delayed response and increased risk.

## Solution
ResponStay provides:
- One-tap SOS alert system
- Real-time monitoring dashboard
- AI-based threat detection
- Emergency service integration

## Features
- Guest mobile app (SOS + alerts)
- Hotel admin dashboard
- AI surveillance system
- Live emergency coordination

## Tech Stack (Prototype)
- Figma (UI Design)
- Canva (Presentation)
- Basic Web / Concept Model

